{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"57056-german","title":"Die Strafe","description":"Was ist die Strafe für den Jungen, der zu viele Früchte aß?","language":"German","langCode":"de","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Apoorva Advant"],"illustrators":["Melany  Pietersen"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/57056-german"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/127094/size3/db95bbe732126e9b7dd459a38227fc1c.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/127094/size6/db95bbe732126e9b7dd459a38227fc1c.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93155/size6/621be475d97687fb130ca0827e87a43b.jpg","text":"Eines Tages brachte Mama verschiedene   Früchte.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93156/size6/8d707c2a78ef1a3d95b1e2589fbd7022.jpg","text":"„Wann dürfen wir einige Früchte essen?“ fragten wir. \n„Wir essen welche heute Nacht,\" sagte Mama.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93157/size6/b3457b880586508bc923dd63a21756cc.jpg","text":"Mein Bruder Rahim ist gierig. \nEr probierte alleFrüchte. \nEr aß viel von denen.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93158/size6/df2d14148444729dab3a976537d7d82f.jpg","text":"„Guck mal, was Rahim getan hat!\" schrie mein jünger Bruder.\n„Rahim ist frech und \nselbstsüchtig,\" sagte ich.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96119/size6/c52875523996cbf9b5b1977b86c867bd.jpg","text":"Mama war auf Rahim böse.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93160/size6/b979f87f4098f2fc901b247a4fb0292e.jpg","text":"Wir waren auch auf Rahim \nböse. \nAber es tat Rahim nicht leid.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93161/size6/037f8113f567639b80b17b8b5242d7bf.jpg","text":"„Bestrafst du Rahim?“ fragte der jüngere Bruder.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93162/size6/0c486900a488206c0241ba6e0631cf0e.jpg","text":"„Rahim, du wirst es bald bedauern,“ warnte Mama.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93163/size6/07cb6e3b6ea2c18d8070115facbe635a.jpg","text":"Rahim begann, sich unwohl zu fühlen.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93164/size6/bedfd6855dcab46e502e87f6da1b1e98.jpg","text":"„Ich habe Bauchschmerzen,“ flüsterte Rahim.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93165/size6/72b70df72bd142036ba49d0bbda8ce0b.jpg","text":"Mama wusste, warum Rahim krank geworden war.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93166/size6/1b0336362b264fe7e48e76ea8a335de0.jpg","text":"Später sagte uns Rahim „Es tut mir leid. \nIch\nwerde nie wieder so gierig sein,“ versprach er.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":118}}